			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Here is my background.  I am a high end raider(currently the highest ranked chanter on my server in eqrankings and in the top 20-30 serverwide).  I have been playing shortly after beta was released and long before RoK was even a pipe dream.  I currently am paying for FOUR accounts and have paid for more then that in the past that I let personal friends take over.
<br />

<br />
You know...I could probobly have lived with some of these nerfs(for a bit) but it's just that charmed put me over the edge.  
<br />
Here are the rest of the reasons that were pushing me out the door...
<br />
 
<br />
Here is what omens ripped from us:
<br />
1) charm nerf - 150ish dps average for omens charm and ALL i repeat ALL 65 and up pre omens content flagged immune.  I'm sorry but when i can go to seb in RoK and charm a juggy that has more dps then a lvl 67 omens mob something is horribly broken.  They hit for 250 and then on break introduce you to your bind point as they got midevil on your buttocks.
<br />
2) pacification nerf - hidden nerf in that placate just eliminates npc assist and does NOT i repeat does NOT allow you to get close or walk by mobs.  Pacification on down works just like it always did it's just placate nerf. 
<br />
3) pbaoe stun nerf - they linked color cloud and color snap so you can only cast one at a time.  When you cast one it grey's out the other.  Also they reduced it to a 6 second stun.  The lame stun is not enough time to recover a pet break or cc any mobs that might have gotten stunned. 
<br />
4) focus item nerf - nerfing all the time effects.  Worse yet, nerfing all the HIGHEST end god content effects(txevu/tacvi).  Then they have the balls to put lvl 70 focus items with elemental stats on easy mobs.  Sorry but I don't understand how you have txevu/tacvi loot that has diminished effects and yet easy, easy, easy content that has lvl 70 effects. 
<br />
5) the horrible horrible horrible spell progression.  Why is our 69th mez buried so deep in turn ins?  Why is our first mez not bought?  Give me a break, they spell progression is seriously fubared. 
<br />
6) no Word of Morrel upgrade or any way to deal with pets on break or A LOT OF MOBS IN CAMP.  This is an absolutely huge nerf and further reduces our cc'ing ability.  
<br />
7) Etheral rune agro issues and well...it's just not enough of an upgrade
<br />
<img src="images/smiles/icon_cool.gif" alt="Cool" border="0" /> Pulled Elrich Rune upgrade before release.
<br />
9) I knew i had more points but am too pissed to think straight.
<br />
 
<br />
Here is what we got in omens:
<br />
1) 20ish percent increase in dps from our 2 new omens nuke -- assuming you get the ancient spell
<br />
2) We get a mez to FINALLY do our job in high end raiding and now xping. 
<br />
3) We get a couple new wow wee buffs of c6/speed upgrade.
<br />
4) I'm actually happy about this - we get a very nice upgrade to zeb but heaven forbid they remove the componant so we can do a secondary role on raiding... 
<br />
5) I'm very very pleased with group alender.
<br />
 
<br />
Aren't we suppose to increase in power in an expansion rather then decrease in power?  I am just beside myself and don't know what else to say. My only response is that I am cancelling all four of my accounts.
<br />
 
<br />
Clot
<br />
Soon to be retired chanter of Mortalis</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
