</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>SoE wrote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote"> You're in our world now </td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
<br />

<br />
Enchanters were never intended to be an offensive class. We've always been needed in raid and group situations as support. I can honestly say I have never seen any one on the luclin server that has met my caliper of being able to control a charm pet in groups. 
<br />

