<br />

<br />
It was fun while it lasted, but every one is making a huge deal about something they said they have been working on since day one of the influx of chanter's using charm DPS.
<br />

<br />
My game isn't ruined, I just found other things to do instead of looking for the easy way out. Gratz me on becoming a raid leader, and a class leader in my guild.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
